@node introduction "Introduction"

Old friend of my brought a new mobile in EraGsm network, saddly new
Era's prefix wasn't accepted by TaskiSms :( I reported that to Pawe¯,
but he was so busy. So I decited to take this job on my own ;-)

This patch will update TaskiSms data files and allow You to send something
to new EraGsm prefix.

@endnode

@node howto "How to apply"

Unpack this archive somewhere. Watch attached png file ;)
Next, copy executable and run it. That's all! Next, go to
@{"Author" link author} section and send me a sms. Since it's
smsware, damn :-)

@endnode

